{
  "texts": [
    "After choosing \"citation\" as the type of analysis and \"documents\" as the unit of analysis, the mini-mum number of citations for a document was set to 7.",
    "This resulted in 20 documents out of the 42 sample documents meeting the threshold.",
    "Table 7 lists a few of the influential articles that were arranged according to their normalized citations.",
    "It is worth noting that only representative articles with normalized citations greater than 2 are listed in Table 7.",
    "Based on Table 7, it is apparent that the total citations and normalized citations counts vary sig-nificantly among the articles in the field of AI-in-CC-in-CI."
  ]
}